title: Eps. 151 - Bosom Buddies
description:
Most people can’t get on because they’re too busy trying to get over. This was the statement that sparked the topic for today’s podcast. Many people have the tendency to overcharge people who they believe have money and can afford it. What they don’t understand is that the person with money knows they’re trying to get over and they are hurting themselves in the long run. ET gives listeners information on how to do business the right way by practicing mutualism and being honest and upfront in the beginning.
